1048
00:54:05,976 --> 00:54:09,605
for working people in America,
to me that's a holy place.

1049
00:54:09,646 --> 00:54:10,806
Let me add to it.

1050
00:54:10,847 --> 00:54:14,874
Over the whole duration of the lraq war
