1054
00:54:25,729 --> 00:54:27,663
The global economy
has never been better

1055
00:54:27,697 --> 00:54:30,325
and the global stock markets
have never been better, Jimmy.

1056
00:54:30,367 --> 00:54:32,392
It is either a God-given miracle

1057
00:54:32,435 --> 00:54:34,403
or it has something to do
with the victories

1058
00:54:34,437 --> 00:54:36,803
of the spreading world
of capitalism or both.

1059
00:54:36,840 --> 00:54:38,774
Moore: They think
Wall Street's a holy place.

1060
00:54:38,808 --> 00:54:41,743
What do you think
