1096
00:56:31,121 --> 00:56:33,612
believe that someday
they will have a chance

1097
00:56:33,656 --> 00:56:36,181
of becoming
well-to-do themselves

1098
00:56:36,226 --> 00:56:39,389
if they just keep trying
