1099
00:56:41,731 --> 00:56:44,029
The wealthy were pleased
that so many people

1100
00:56:44,067 --> 00:56:46,900
had bought in
to the American Dream

1101
00:56:46,936 --> 00:56:49,996
while they, the rich,
had no intention

1102
00:56:50,039 --> 00:56:52,940
of ever sharing it with anyone.

1103
00:56:52,976 --> 00:56:56,275
I think capitalism is a lot more
