1105
00:56:58,715 --> 00:57:02,310
I always say that democracy is--
can be two wolves and a sheep

1106
00:57:02,352 --> 00:57:04,013
deciding on what to have
for dinner.

1107
00:57:04,053 --> 00:57:07,284
Moore: This is Stephen Moore--
no relation--

1108
00:57:07,323 --> 00:57:09,757
a columnist
