00:58:10,487 --> 00:58:13,752
In fact, all I saw
was "We the people,"

1130
00:58:13,790 --> 00:58:16,384
something about
"a more perfect union,"

1131
00:58:16,426 --> 00:58:19,793
and "promoting
the general welfare."

1132
00:58:19,829 --> 00:58:24,323
Welfare, union, we?

1133
00:58:24,367 --> 00:58:26,767
That sounded like that other -ism.

1134
00:58:26,803 --> 00:58:30,239
But no, that's democracy.

1135
00:58:30,273 --> 00:58:31,975
And I began to wonder,
"What would it be like

