1152
00:59:17,687 --> 00:59:20,520
Man: And it's a democratically-run
operation where every member

1153
00:59:20,557 --> 00:59:23,526
has one vote and an equal say.

1154
00:59:23,560 --> 00:59:25,824
- All in favor?
- All in favor?

1155
00:59:25,862 --> 00:59:28,888
Man: It takes the money
out of the equation.

1156
00:59:28,932 --> 00:59:30,957
Moore: By taking the money
out of the equation

1157
00:59:31,000 --> 00:59:33,230
so that they can call the shots,

1158
00:59:33,269 --> 00:59:35,601
they end up making more money.

1159
00:59:35,638 --> 00:59:38,266
Cool, huh?

1160
00:59:41,945 --> 00:59:44,743
And how patriotic
that they want to extend

1161
00:59:44,781 --> 00:59:48,615
their love of American democracy
