1730
01:26:21,748 --> 01:26:25,582
when he left Goldman
to go and run the Treasury Department.

1731
01:26:25,618 --> 01:26:29,418
I think we saw the best of
the United States of America

1732
01:26:29,455 --> 01:26:32,856
in the Speaker's
office tonight.

1733
01:26:32,892 --> 01:26:35,884
Moore:
The best of America?

1734
01:26:35,929 --> 01:26:39,831
Or did he mean
the best of Goldman Sachs?

1735
