01:29:36,309 --> 01:29:39,005
People understand that
the House of Representatives

1802
01:29:39,045 --> 01:29:41,673
needs to pass this piece
of legislation.

1803
01:29:41,714 --> 01:29:44,649
Mr. Speaker, my message
to the American people...

1804
01:29:44,684 --> 01:29:47,676
don't let Congress
seal this Wall Street deal.

1805
01:29:47,720 --> 01:29:50,280
These criminals have
so much political power

1806
01:29:50,323 --> 01:29:52,757
